{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"116158e716","title":"给续范亭\"的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"84288b78d2","index":0,"year":1947,"month":2,"day":2,"articleId":"116158e716"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f63c07699f","type":"paragraph","text":"给续范亭\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"},{"id":"d8df0c471c","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年2月2日）范亭兄左右：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"},{"id":"e2fd381eed","type":"paragraph","text":"大示早已接读，奖她极多，自当努力以副期望。闻贵盖减轻，增加食量，每日能走若干步，真是一大快事。致邓函已看过，词严义正，发人深省。最近刘绍庭以兄来电述及邓之方针，部意以为可以同意，暂时各守原防，将来再决进止。目前时局，邓之地位，只能做到这一步。各区作战日有起色，击破蒋氏进攻是可能的。惟蒋尚欲孤注一挪，集中四五十个团于徐州附近，欲在山东决一胜负，我方现正准备迎击中。边区局势现较平稳，如缓德方面住得相直，似不必去普西北，增加劳顿，如何尚析的定。敬颂康吉！","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"},{"id":"89c00f7a26","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东上","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"},{"id":"7be0c6ceee","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四七年二月二日[1]续范亭（1893-1947），山西省婷县（今原平市）西社村人，著名爱国将领。早年参加孙中山领导的同题会。后在国民党任职，曾经隐退一段时间，后与共产党人合作创建山西新军。1947年病逝后被追认为中国共产党正式党员。121指邓宝班，当时任普陕绥边区总司令","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"},{"id":"5dc2731b44","type":"paragraph","text":"日简起色，整成示风道雅色如龙表","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"},{"id":"35d64bdca3","type":"paragraph","text":"的。表数数在注哪其大不平以握谨要感极系，同者","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"},{"id":"25beb0b512","type":"paragraph","text":"2十个国持核州你区，教空有行力人司明情。到责三","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"},{"id":"240e800a3d","type":"paragraph","text":"长一腾员，我考配两旺整我形食量，民回的支关于完直是","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"},{"id":"1582f5beaf","type":"paragraph","text":"中心确大妆手。或新面常遇方","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"},{"id":"c4edd31772","type":"paragraph","text":"德方面住律想宜心小交费绿民山食人理航家运地","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"},{"id":"467f5c0503","type":"paragraph","text":"置北，代应劳线以吃尚青为航达成东支方钟，就以少","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"},{"id":"8fb46deadb","type":"paragraph","text":"的的定敬硕和人国高婷变完质运心","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"},{"id":"74e3f3b64a","type":"paragraph","text":"最完！上请点上再决化业。司前开与节","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"},{"id":"b1e60ff176","type":"paragraph","text":"信，只能破到辽一岁。考函旅我毛泽东致续范亭信的手稿","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716"}],"page":{"id":"ddfe89e49c","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"116158e716","start":416,"end":417}}}},"__N_SSG":true}